- [Rhythm Formant Analysis](https://github.com/dafyddg/RFA) from Dafydd Gibbon
- [Temporal Modulation Spectrum Toolbox](https://github.com/LeoVarnet/TMST) (Matlab code) from L√©o Varnet 

